WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:02.000
ជម្រាបសួរ Good Morning everyone.

2
00:00:02.001 --> 00:00:04.000
My name is Nan Munireachh Vityea,

3
00:00:04.001 --> 00:00:07.000
a Grade 12 student from Indradevy High School

4
00:00:07.001 --> 00:00:10.000
in Phnom Penh, Cambodia.

5
00:00:10.001 --> 00:00:13.999
I'm here to express my sincere interest

6
00:00:14.000 --> 00:00:19.001
in applying for Asia Youth Leaders 2026.

7
00:00:19.002 --> 00:00:23.050
My interest in this program stems from a genuine belief

8
00:00:23.051 --> 00:00:26.050
that the most meaningful connections,

9
00:00:26.051 --> 00:00:30.050
solutions are built not in isolations,

10
00:00:30.050 --> 00:00:32.050
but rather through connection.

11
00:00:32.051 --> 00:00:34.999
Asia Youth Leaders 2026

12
00:00:35.000 --> 00:00:37.000
brings together young people

13
00:00:37.001 --> 00:00:39.000
from across Asia

14
00:00:39.001 --> 00:00:41.000
to discuss real problems

15
00:00:41.001 --> 00:00:42.050
and propose real answers

16
00:00:42.051 --> 00:00:43.999
and that is exactly

17
00:00:44.000 --> 00:00:45.001
the kind of environment

18
00:00:45.002 --> 00:00:48.050
I want to be a part of.

19
00:00:48.051 --> 00:00:50.001
I have always admired

20
00:00:50.002 --> 00:00:54.001
how Japanese people approach social responsibility

21
00:00:54.002 --> 00:00:56.999
not as an obligation, but

22
00:00:57.000 --> 00:01:00.000
as a natural extension of who they are.

23
00:01:00.001 --> 00:01:02.050
I have seen this firsthand

24
00:01:02.050 --> 00:01:05.050
through Japanese volunteers and organizations

25
00:01:05.050 --> 00:01:07.000
active here in Cambodia,

26
00:01:07.001 --> 00:01:10.000
who work quietly and consistently

27
00:01:10.001 --> 00:01:13.000
to benefit communities beyond their own.

28
00:01:13.001 --> 00:01:15.999
That spirit of contribution

29
00:01:16.000 --> 00:01:17.999
is something I deeply respect

30
00:01:18.000 --> 00:01:20.999
and want to learn from directly.

31
00:01:21.000 --> 00:01:23.050
Returning from this program,

32
00:01:23.050 --> 00:01:26.999
I intend to share everything I learn

33
00:01:27.000 --> 00:01:29.050
with my classmates, my school

34
00:01:29.051 --> 00:01:31.999
and my broader community.

35
00:01:32.000 --> 00:01:36.999
Knowledge that stays with one person only helps one person.

36
00:01:37.000 --> 00:01:39.999
Knowledge that spreads will help a country.

37
00:01:40.000 --> 00:01:43.999
I am ready to listen, to contribute, and to grow.

38
00:01:44.000 --> 00:01:47.000
Thank you for this opportunity.